Mutant monster 3 - https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/da19877e1beb4a75b8f42be761e3c0c9

Low poly mutant monster model ideal for extras or boss. An interesting idea for both heads and weapons.

The project has 4 body texture options and 2 weapon texture options. This model is also modular. You can remove the teeth tongue, and eyes.
